Package com.genologics.ri.process

Class Summary
ArtifactLink Artifact is a child element of input-output-map and provides a link to an Artifact that was either an input or output of the Process for the input-output-map.
GenologicsProcess The detailed representation of a process.
GenologicsProcesses The representation of a list of process links.
InputOutputMap Input-output-map is a child element of Process and relates one of the Process inputs to one of the outputs that was produced for that input.
InstrumentLink The instrument element provides a URI to the instrument that is responsible for running the process.
ObjectFactory This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the com.genologics.ri.process package.
Parameter The parameter is a child element of process that integrates the Process with the External Program Integration plug-in (EPP).
ParentProcessLink Parent-process is a child element of Artifact and provides a URI linking to the Process that created the Artifact.
ProcessLink Process-link is a child element type of process and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of a process.
ProcessTypeLink Process-type is a child element of process that identifies and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of the process type that the process is associated with.
Technician Technician is a child element of Process and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of the technician that ran the Process.
 

Enum Summary
OutputGenerationType
